## Data / Data Access

### Dataset Used

This project uses the MNIST dataset of handwritten digits:

- 60,000 training images
- 10,000 test images
- 10 classes (digits 0–9)
- Grayscale images
- Image size: 28×28 pixels

---

### Data Loading

The dataset is automatically downloaded using torchvision:

```python
torchvision.datasets.MNIST(
    root='./data',
    train=True,
    transform=transform,
    download=True
)
